  23:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****                    ##### Flash Extension features #####
  24:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  25:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** 
  26:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   [..] Comparing to other previous devices, the FLASH interface for STM32H5xx
  27:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        devices contains the following additional features
  28:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** 
  29:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Capacity up to 2 Mbyte with dual bank architecture supporting read-while-write
ARM GAS  C:\Users\DELL\AppData\Local\Temp\ccTERXlg.s 			page 2


  30:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****            capability (RWW)
  31:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Dual bank memory organization
  32:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Product State protection
  33:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Write protection
  34:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Secure access only protection
  35:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Bank / register swapping (when Dual-Bank)
  36:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Watermark-based secure protection
  37:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Block-based secure protection
  38:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Block-based privilege protection
  39:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (+) Hide Protection areas
