 158:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @brief  Perform a mass erase or erase the specified FLASH memory sectors
 159:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @param[in]  pEraseInit pointer to an FLASH_EraseInitTypeDef structure that
