 162:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @param[out]  SectorError pointer to variable that contains the configuration
 163:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *          information on faulty sector in case of error (0xFFFFFFFF means that all
